\v 2 to proclaimВҰ304470 to Yerushalem'sВҰ304473 earsВҰ304471:
\q1 вҖңYahwehВҰ304477 saysВҰ304476: I rememberВҰ304478 your loyalВҰ304480 commitment \add вүҲwhen you were all young\add*
